\id 2PE
\h 2 PITA
\toc1 2 Pita
\toc2 2 Pita
\toc3 2 Pita
\mt1 2 Pita
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Aya Simon Pita, Jesus Kristus nẽ ferfer fen aposel,
\p idi neda Negur ado Isennadaya, Jesus Kristus nẽ madur bagai bunem momoiya meli bagai neda gen dalen anidi bun, pas enei atotof.
\p 
\v 2 Ã, Negur ado neda Odug Jesus nigin keleĩ bunem, wau ifenẽya ado wau inosiya ã bun barikãf.
\s1 Negur Ĩ Ada Yogon Igirnadan
\p 
\v 3 Negur ĩ yogon fula fiya medeĩya ado biya bunem iweignadan, ada ĩ nigin keleĩ bunem, ada Negur nẽ oroya bun mata tabodõf nigin, ereb lau tafef anĩ ganan yogon megeir anim ifanadan.
\v 4 Enei bunem, ĩ ada yogon promis od, odug fen meli bagai andi ifanadan, are anĩ bunem ã Negur nẽ tobonunã bun bagai ufareg fen, bouwa nẽ oroya sanem teneub ganan daũ fen anĩ utorõgouf nigin age fen.
\p 
\v 5 Age fiya nigin, ãgenei momoiya bun, biya anĩ tobol fiya nigin kabĩ totol walogouf, agog fen, biya bun, keleĩ tobol fiya nigin,
\v 6 agog fen, keleĩ bun, aug nigin biya kulatun ibodõya tobol fiya nigin, agog fen, aug nigin biya kulatun ibodõya bun, feseya sã ifareya tobol fiya nigin, agog fen, feseya sã ifareya bun, Negur nẽ oroya bun ibodõya tobol fiya nigin,
\v 7 agog fen, Negur nẽ oroya bun ibodõya bun, abob geid nigal yũya tobol fiya nigin, agog fen, abob geid nigal yũya bun, wau laa fiya tobol fiya nigin kabĩ totol walogouf.
\v 8 Ere nigin, ã tobonunã enei ganan waleg fen, tobol gouf are, ã neda Odug Jesus Kristus nigin keleĩ yaleya bun kabĩ biya kaũ ado walogouf.
\v 9 Anĩ ere, taka ĩ eneidi taka to yalouf, ĩ melsã nigin dogol ileya kisi feleya fen, mala ifofakeleya, agef fen, ĩ yogon mosor kulu tamal bun tamal lilik fiyekelen anĩ weder tu kelen.
\p 
\v 10 Anĩ nigin, turau tar, Negurem ã iweignei ken, igirnein anĩ tutuk bagai keleĩ youf nigin, kabĩ totol walogouf. Ere nigin, ã enei ago gouf are, ã to bagai kubũ gouf.
\v 11 Ago ge di, ã, neda Odug fen Isennadaya, Jesus Kristus nẽ tano mata gai ibodkeleya bun, ileya nigin lakĩ fiya taka to ibodõf.
\s1 Negur Nẽ Itotoya Nẽ Profet Od
\p 
\v 12 Anĩ nigin, ã enei nigin kelei ken, momoiya ã gama ado anĩ bun totol ufaregef, anĩ ere, aya enei nigin kisi gouf nigin, faimud wedereĩ fokõ afouf.
\v 13 Aya kisi afef, aya bouwau enei nẽ salafat bun abod mog, ãgenei kisi turĩ afouf, are tutuk,
\v 14 ere nigin, aya mogo, neda Odug Jesus Kristus kurõ feis irokanan nigin, aya keleĩ, aya mogo melsã yerin awaikalauf.
\v 15 Anĩ nigin, aya ã atorneĩ mog, ã faimud enei karĩ walagauf nigin kabĩ totol alouf.
\p 
\v 16 Amã, neda Odug Jesus Kristus nẽ megeir ado isiya nigin ã marokenein sain are, amã nemã kisim tamo nẽ nenerĩ anĩ to wogõ mayein, anĩ ere, amã malamam bagai yogon fula fiya medeĩya nẽ megeir mailen anĩ wogõ maun.
\v 17 Ait are Negur fula fiya medeĩya megeir ado bunem ĩ bun isi fen, iron, “Eĩ neu Kesu, ĩ nigin aya wau laa fedig, ĩ nigin aya wau kulĩ yedig,”\f + \fr 1:17 \ft Matyu 17:5; Mak 9:7; Luk 9:35\f* sain anĩ bun, ĩ, Tama Negur bunem, yana odug ado fula fiya medeĩya yalen.
\v 18 Amã ĩ geid arei fateul bun mafar mog, ait enei saa ilunem isi mog, amã mug bagai karĩ maun.
\p 
\v 19 Agef fen, ada, profet neid od are momoi anĩ, megeir tafe, momoi tauf, are lalan gugum modoũ bun, we fef ile, we kasasa fe fen, bonimei nẽ barisa wauĩ bun fã youf gen, ã profet neid od karĩ weleg fen, el ge dõ gouf are, ã biya ubodõgouf.
\v 20 Ereb odug bagai are eig fiya, ã keleĩ youf, Negur nẽ Itotoya nẽ profet od taka, tamo nẽ kisim to faded fouf.
\v 21 Ere nigin, profet od, tamo nẽ oroya bunem to wogõ den, anĩ ere, tamo Awa Uur Fateulem ulum iroukenẽdi di, Negur bun tamal od dale fen, wogõ den.
\c 2
\s1 Idegẽya Tise Ado Idi Daũ Fediya Nigin
\p 
\v 1 Anĩ ere, tamo kayau atun idegẽya profeteg difaren, age fiya gen, ã atun idegẽya tiseg dibodõf. Idi fau tamo kayau daũ fediya nẽ idegẽya od anĩ iminẽyan difelneĩf, Odug na yaledin ĩ anĩ wa de fen, idi dogo bun kaisã bagai daũ feidleya anĩ dinouf.
\v 2 Musei dogo neid tobonuneid sane dõ de fen, momoi nẽ naab are naabura gudũ difouf.
\v 3 Dogo naumeid nigin, tise eneidi nenerĩ dogo neid kisim wogõ diyei ken, safineĩ gei difouf. Negur idi mogo es fedin, agef fen, idi daũ fediya nẽ are mogo isiyouf.
\p 
\v 4 Negur ĩ engel mosor dino di, to isenneĩd fen, hel bun sur fiyẽdin, dumen es fediyouf nigin ku gugum keleya bun inenẽdin.
\v 5 Negur ĩ kulu tenebur nẽ tamo kayau to isenneĩd fen, tamo kayau idi Negur nẽ to difaren anidi bun kuwei sur fen, anĩ ere, ĩ, Noa madur bagai nigin wogõya tamo ado, sewen anidi geid ahaha fedin.
\v 6 Negur ĩ, Sodom taun ado Gomora taun, yam yakur feid aasu ileya bunem daũ feidlen, are tamo kayau Negur nẽ to difaref anidi bun, ereb wõ youf anĩ ifelnẽdiyouf nigin age fen.
\v 7 Negur ĩ, Lot madur tamo, tamo lo to dõ difedig anidi neid tobonuneid sane nigin wau morõdig ĩ ahaha fiyen
\v 8 (ere nigin, madur tamo are, naa ganan bun, idi atun ibod ken, tobonuneid sane ilen ado karĩ yen anĩ bunem, yogon malakanon madur anĩ darau yalen).
\v 9 Age fiyauf are, Odug ĩ naig fe fen, tamo Negur nẽ dibodok anidi, morõ bun tamal yalelneĩd fen, tamo Negur nẽ to dibodok anidi, darau bun irounẽdif ile, es fiya nẽ naa bun ileya nigin anĩ keleĩ.
\v 10 Negur ĩ, idi bouwa nẽ oroya sane dõ de fen, Odug nẽ yana lai difedig anidi bun, momoi bagai age fouf.
\p Idi kumĩ sã ado, dogo yeneid dalesedig. Idi, engel megeir adodo nigin bou yũya od wogõya nigin to kumĩ dedig.
\v 11 Anĩ ere, engeleg dogo neid totol ado megeir odug bagai nigin tamo eneidi wal fediya, Odug mala bun, engel megeir adodo age fediya nigin bou yũya od to wogõ dedig.
\v 12 Anĩ ere, tamo eneidi, ereb idi keleĩ sã nigin kono difedig. Idi gaar kuĩ kisi sã, bouwa nẽ oroya dogol dõ dife di, tamom kaka difeid fen, didenkesiyouf nigin dogol gõ difedidig anidi gen. Gaar kuĩ gen, idig daũ fediyouf.
\p 
\v 13 Idi sane age difen kilei, mala solo sane dalouf. Idi gaa atun bouwa nẽ oroya sigigi fiya nigin orodidig. Idi amuyẽ ado gerĩ tõ fiya. Idi ã geid sifa dino fen, nedi bouweid nẽ oroya sigigi difedig.
\v 14 Idi meleid bun seseirã tobonunã barikã ado fen, mosor inoya nigin to bagai ditorõdig. Idi, tamo kayau totol sã difaref anidi, didĩ difedidig. Idi safina musei youf nigin imeid su lai de fen sũ we fiya nigin keleĩ bagai. Idi daũ feidleya nẽ gere tar.
\v 15 Idi naab madur anĩ ditor ken, Beor naal, Balam ĩ sane nẽ mala solo nigin wau laa fedig anĩ nẽ naab dõ difouf nigin fasis difen.
\v 16 Anĩ ere, ĩ donki, gaar kuĩ wogõya kisi feleya sã anim, yogon kũ fenẽya nigin ou fiyen, donki ĩ tamo nẽ ait nem wogõ ye fen, profet anĩ nẽ neneya kisi katũ fiyen.
\p 
\v 17 Tamo eneidi, naan warur gere keleya gen ado, ogou uyẽ yau totol ado bunem irou isidig gen. Modoũ gugum keleya bagai anĩ, idi nigin saia fen.
\v 18 Idi yana yaleseya od kaũ sã wogõ de fen, tamo kayau idi kũ fenẽya bun dibodok anidi bun tamal, mogo diyawof anidi, bouwa nẽ oroya, noli nigin kisi fãya bunem didĩ difedidig.
\v 19 Tamo sane eneidi, tamo kayau karika ibodõya mafeneĩf de dirokenẽdidig, anĩ ere, idi dogo sane nẽ ferfer, ere nigin, tamo ĩ, ereb ĩ wal fiyek anĩ nẽ ferfer.
\v 20 Idi, neda Odug ado Isennadaya, Jesus Kristus kelei ken, tenebur nẽ sane bun tamal soso dife di, baban tenebur nẽ sanem fili feid fen, wal fediyouf are, idi gariya bun sane dibodon anĩ wal fiya, idikeleya bun sane bagai dibodõf.
\v 21 Idi madur bagai nẽ naab anĩ kelei ken, ĩtãfiya fateul idi imeid bun dinon anĩ dudum difem are, idi madur bagai nẽ naab anĩ to keleim, are dem.
\v 22 Od biya tamo kayau wogõ dedig are, idi nigin momoi, “Gaũ yogon iluf anĩ kel yõdig,”\f + \fr 2:22 \ft Proveb 26:11\f* takag, “Bor naan igu kel fen, baban ile ed igũdig.”
\c 3
\s1 Odug Nẽ Naa
\p 
\v 1 Turau tar oboiyou, eĩ neu pas baban ã bun sur afef. Aya pas uru enei atotodin are, kisi biya turĩ akeneĩ di, wedereĩ fokõ youf nigin age afen.
\v 2 Aya, od profet fateul kulu wogõ den ado, ĩtãfiya neda Odug ado Isennadaya, ãgenei aposel bunem ifenein anĩ, ã karĩ walagauf nigin orouf.
\p 
\v 3 Ã uyulil enei keleĩ youf, idikeleya naa bun, kono temeleid disiyouf, idi disi, kono de fen, dogo neid oroya sane dõ difouf.
\v 4 Idi dirõf, “Ĩ asiyouf yen promis od anĩ nain? Amã nemã tamamã tar gare den bunem isif, ereb ereb ganan uruwa bun kare fen gen, agef yenek.”
\v 5 Anĩ ere, idi, kulu bagai Negur nẽ od bunem saa wõ ye fen, teneub naan bun tamal ado naan nem kare fen anĩ, karĩ del fen, wedereid tu kelen.
\v 6 Naan anim, kuwei fã ye fen, sain anĩ bun teneub ganan daũ felen.
\v 7 Od de anim, saa ado teneub gama tailef are, yã nigin faraf foi fen, agef fen, tamo kayau momoiya sã es fiya ado daũ feidleya nẽ naa nigin inon ibodok.
\p 
\v 8 Anĩ ere, turau tar oboiyou, ereb tekelei enei to wedereĩ tu kalauf, Odug bun naa tekelei are tausen yar gen, agef fen, tausen yar are naa tekelei gen.
\v 9 Odug ĩ, yogon promis od kisi falauf nigin, tunĩ age dedig gen, to foi yedig. Ĩ taka daũ feleyan ileya itor ken, ganan waud falei fouf nigin, sain meluk tari yeĩdig.
\p 
\v 10 Anĩ ere, Odug nẽ naa are, bẽ tamo gen isiyouf. Saa gududũ ye fen, iwaikalauf, ereb ereb nanaal teneub inon are ganan yam daũ falauf, agef fen, teneub ado ereb ereb ganan ĩ bun ibodok are yaor fouf.\f + \fr 3:10 \ft Itotoya tunĩ eig de ditoton: \fq are yakur falauf\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 11 Naab enei bun, ereb ereb ganan daũ falauf, anĩ nigin, ã tamo kayau naig fiya bagai wõya nigin kisi gef? Ã fateul ubodõg fen, Negur nẽ tobonunã bun ubodõgouf.
\v 12 Ã, Negur nẽ naa tarig fen, kaisã bagai isiyouf nigin ololo gouf. Naa anĩ bun, yam saa daũ falauf, ereb ereb nanaal teneub inon are uruwam naan kalauf.
\v 13 Anĩ ere, ada yogon promis od tarou fen, saa mata ado teneub mata ololo tafef, are madur tamo kayau an dibodõf.
\p 
\v 14 Age fiya nigin, turau tar oboiyou, ã enei tari gef nigin, Odug mala bun amuyẽ sã, od sã wowãg fen, ĩ ado wauĩ katõ gouf nigin kabĩ totol walogouf.
\v 15 Ãgenei kisi bun, neda Odug sain meluk tari fiya are, kel yaleya nigin gouf, are neda turada oboida Pol ĩg Negur kisi biya ifenẽ di, ã bun pas itoton kilei.
\v 16 Ĩ yogon pas ganan bun, eig fe itotoid fen, enei nigin wogõ yen. Yogon pas bun, ereb ereb tunĩ keleĩya nigin lakĩ fiya bagai ibodok, are idi keleĩ sa ken, momoiya ilef isif anidi, Negur nẽ Itotoya tunĩ bun age difedig gen, falei difeid fen, dogo daũ feidleya bun diledig.
\p 
\v 17 Anĩ nigin, turau tar oboiyou, ã enei mogo keleĩ nigin, lo wal fiya tamo neid kũ fenẽyam to guri diyei ken, dile ãgenei modoũ biya utorõg fen, kubũ geya nigin lo welegei.
\v 18 Anĩ ere, neda Odug ado Isennadaya, Jesus Kristus nẽ wau ifenẽya ado keleĩ bun, odugouf. Ĩ bun fula fiya medeĩya gama ado faimud ibodkalauf! Momoi. 
